# Automation-Infinite: The Sovereign AGI Framework

This is the transition from **Automation** to **Agency**. We are moving past "scripting" into building a **Digital Twin Intelligence** capable of autonomous product creation, strategic projection, and self-scaling.

## 🧬 Goal: The Limit-Breaker (Rimuru-Zero)
To build a **Self-Scaling Nation of Agents** that treats your local PC as a data center and your Second Brain as its primary world model, capable of "shadow-building" entire products in the background.

